<div class="flex flex-col bg-white">
  <div class="relative h-[90dvh] w-full">
    <%= video_tag(["iehhero.mp4"], :class => "h-full w-full object-cover", :autoplay => true, :loop => true, :muted => true) %>
    <div class="flex w-full h-full z-10 absolute top-0 left-0 bg-black/40">
      <div class="flex p-2 items-center absolute top-2 right-10">
        <%= image_tag 'svg/marks/namefull.svg', class:"h-12" %>
        <%= image_tag 'svg/marks/transp1.svg', class:"h-14 rounded" %>
      </div>
      <section class="container mx-auto flex flex-col justify-between py-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl xl:text-8xl font-black text-white tracking-tight xl:w-5/12 mt-8">Good design cuts costs, not corners.</h2>
        <div class="xl:w-1/3">
          <p class="text-lg text-white font-semibold leading-7 bg-black/20 p-2 rounded-md mt-2">
            We don't have to sacrifice quality to guarantee our price.
            We source directly from manufacturers, build around your needs, and do it right the first time.
            <br><br>
            It's no secret, just common sense.
            <br><br>
            Get a quote today and join over 7,000 families and businesses who saved two ways with SolarTech.
          </p>
          <div class="flex self-end gap-4 items-center mt-2">
            <p class="text-xl font-black text-white">808-456-6254</p>
            <button class="bg-sitesecond text-white font-bold m-[2px] px-4 py-2 max-w-fit">Get a Quote</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="w-full bg-sitemain relative h-[28rem]">
    <ul class="container mx-auto flex justify-center items-center gap-4 text-lg h-full"> 
      <li class="w-1/3 z-50">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 m-2 text-white bg-black/60 rounded p-2">
          <h4>New Solar</h4>
          <p>
            If you want a lower bill, protection from power outages, or just to help the environment,
            we make it easier than ever. <br>
            We handle permits and approvals, help you with incentive programs, and stand behind our installations with full guarantees.
            All you need to do is turn it on.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="w-1/3 z-50">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 m-2 text-white bg-black/60 rounded p-2">
          <h4>Upgrades</h4>
          <p>
            When your life grows, we can help your system keep up. 
            <br>
            Our inspections are free, and we do NEM upgrades, modular battery storage, microinverters, panels, and more. 
            We try to preserve the equipment you already paid for. We'll talk about your recent power needs, and find the smallest change that meets them.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="w-1/3 z-50">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 m-2 text-white bg-black/60 rounded p-2">
          <h4>Service</h4>
          <p>
            20 years is a long time on any rooftop.
            <br>
            If your system is showing its age, or you need warranty service, we have over 10 years of experience servicing all kinds of hardware.
            Even if we didn't install it, we've seen it before.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="absolute inset-y-0 inset-x-0 container mx-auto flex justify-center items-center gap-4 shadow-lg h-full">
      <div class="w-1/3 h-3/4">
        <%= image_tag 'svg/houses/h11.svg', class:"h-full" %>
      </div>
      <div class="w-1/3 h-3/4">
        <%= image_tag 'svg/houses/h11.svg', class:"h-full" %>
      </div>
      <div class="w-1/3 h-3/4">
        <%= image_tag 'svg/houses/h11.svg', class:"h-full" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="w-full bg-white" data-controller="calculator">

  <%= image_tag 'svg/separators/roofwhite.svg', class:"-mt-4"%>
  </section>

  <div class="flex items-center w-11/12 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-slate-300 rounded-md relative -mt-2">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-end">
      <div class="flex w-full py-12 sm:w-3/4 md:w-7/8 justify-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 sm:w-5/6 px-4 font-montserrat font-semibold text-sitedark text-lg md:text-xl pt-[15dvh] sm:pt-0"> 
          <h4 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl ml-4 sm:ml-0 font-bold text-sitemain tracking-tight">Our approach.</h4>
          <p class="w-5/6 lg:w-2/3 ml-8 md:ml-12 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base">
            We have always focused on friendly service and providing the best value you can find in the state. We go direct to the manufacturers so we never have to compromise on quality. We use durable, modular equipment that's easy to upgrade down the line and you can monitor everything right on your phone.
            <br><br>
            If anything does go wrong, we are also one of the largest service providers in Hawaii. We've seen your problem before, and we are always here to help.
          </p>
          <%= link_to 'Contact Us', home_service_path, class:"rounded-sm bg-sitesecond text-white text-base font-bold px-4 py-2 max-w-fit self-end mr-16 md:mr-24 xl:mr-[20%]" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <%= image_tag 'used/using/oahupv.jpg', class:"absolute top-0 start-0 w-full sm:w-1/4 h-[15dvh] sm:h-full object-cover" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag 'svg/separators/roofmain.svg', class:"mt-4"%>
  <div class="w-full bg-sitemain -mt-2">
    <div class="mt-8 self-end flex items-center w-11/12 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-slate-300 rounded-md relative mb-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="flex w-full py-12 sm:w-3/4 md:w-7/8 justify-center">
          <div class="flex flex-col text-start gap-12 sm:w-5/6 ml-4 pr-4 font-montserrat font-semibold text-sitedark text-lg md:text-xl pt-[15dvh] sm:pt-0"> 
            <h4 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl ml-4 sm:ml-0 font-bold text-sitemain tracking-tight">Our process.</h4>
            <p class="w-5/6 lg:w-2/3 ml-8 md:ml-12 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base">
              One of our local consultants will have a meeting with you to discuss what you want out of a solar system and your power use over the past year. They'll take that information and design a system that meets the goals you set. You may have a few options, but once you find a plan that you like, we take it from there.
              <br><br>
              We prepare and submit all the applications and approvals needed by the city and state. Their turnaround is usually 4-6 weeks long.
              <br><br>
              When approval comes back, we can schedule the installation and all you have to do is turn it on a few days later. You can download the monitoring app for your phone, but we keep an eye on your system for you and we'll let you know if we see a problem.
            </p>
            <%= link_to 'Learn More', home_service_path, class:"rounded-sm bg-sitesecond text-white text-base font-bold px-4 py-2 max-w-fit self-end mr-16 md:mr-24 xl:mr-[20%]" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <%= image_tag 'used/using/oahupv.jpg', class:"absolute top-0 end-0 sm:right-0 w-full sm:w-1/4 h-[15dvh] sm:h-full object-cover" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>